            "code": "\ttypes \u003d []\n\tfor extype in value:\n\t\tif extype.active \u003d\u003d True:\n\t\t\ttypes.append({\u0027label\u0027: extype.name,\u0027value\u0027: extype.extensionTypeUUID})\n\treturn types",
